<L>__{exterior children's orphanage day later}
<A>__{sam sitting alone, lost to the world around him. deng approaches. neither one acknowledging the other for a long beat until...}
<C>__{deng}
<D>__{do you hear that, preacher?}
<C>__{sam}
<D>__{what?}
<C>__{deng}
<D>__{there is no more laughter. the children do not play here anymore. they are scared once again.}
<P>__{(beat)}
<D>__{but now they are scared of you.}
<A>__{sam, no response.}
<C>__{deng }
<D>__{the men do not trust you any longer to lead them into battle. they say you have a wish to die.}
<P>__{(beat)}
<D>__{i am worried about my friend. i want to help him.}
<C>__{sam}
<D>__{i don't need your help.}
<A>__{and sam turns away. after a beat deng walks off, leaving him alone once again.}
